#: ../../advanced/i18n.md:1
msgid "Internationalization (i18n)"
msgstr "国际化（i18n）"

#: ../../advanced/i18n.md:3
msgid ""
"This documentation site is built with Sphinx. Multi-language support uses "
"Sphinx gettext catalogs (`.po` files)."
msgstr ""
"本文档站使用 Sphinx 构建。多语言支持通过 Sphinx 的 gettext 目录（`.po` 文件）"
"实现。"

#: ../../advanced/i18n.md:5
msgid "Current setup"
msgstr "当前设置"

#: ../../advanced/i18n.md:7
msgid "Default language: English (`en`) at site root"
msgstr "默认语言：英文（`en`），发布在站点根目录"

#: ../../advanced/i18n.md:8
msgid "Chinese (Simplified): `zh_CN` published under `/zh/`"
msgstr "简体中文：`zh_CN`，发布在 `/zh/`"

#: ../../advanced/i18n.md:9
msgid "Translation files live in `code/docs/locale/<lang>/LC_MESSAGES/`"
msgstr "翻译文件位于 `code/docs/locale/<lang>/LC_MESSAGES/`"

#: ../../advanced/i18n.md:11
msgid ""
"GitHub Pages builds both languages in `code/.github/workflows/pages.yml`."
msgstr ""
"GitHub Pages 会在 `code/.github/workflows/pages.yml` 中同时构建两种语言。"

#: ../../advanced/i18n.md:13
msgid ""
"This site also includes a global language switcher (top-right on every page) "
"implemented via Sphinx template overrides under `code/docs/_templates/`."
msgstr ""
"本站还包含全站语言切换（每页右上角），通过 `code/docs/_templates/` 下的 "
"Sphinx 模板覆盖实现。"

#: ../../advanced/i18n.md:15
msgid "First-principles translation guidelines (for consistency)"
msgstr "第一性原理翻译指南（保证一致性）"

#: ../../advanced/i18n.md:17
msgid ""
"To keep the Chinese site **elegant, coherent, and context-consistent**, "
"treat translation as a *semantic mapping* rather than a word-for-word "
"rewrite:"
msgstr ""
"为了让中文站点**优雅、连贯、上下文一致**，请把翻译当作“语义映射”，而不是逐词改写："

#: ../../advanced/i18n.md:19
msgid ""
"**Preserve meaning first**: keep definitions, constraints, and caveats "
"intact; avoid “free” paraphrasing that changes technical intent."
msgstr "**先保真**：保持定义、约束与注意事项不走样；避免改变技术意图的“自由”改写。"

#: ../../advanced/i18n.md:20
msgid ""
"**Keep structure stable**: don’t reorder sections or rewrite headings into "
"new concepts; mirroring the English information architecture keeps "
"navigation and cross-page references consistent."
msgstr ""
"**结构稳定**：不要重新排序章节或把标题改写成新概念；保持与英文信息架构一致，有助于导航与跨页引用一致。"

#: ../../advanced/i18n.md:21
msgid ""
"**Translate user-facing text, not code**: do *not* translate tool names, "
"parameter names, file paths, environment variables, or code blocks."
msgstr "**翻译面向用户的文字，不翻译代码**：不要翻译工具名、参数名、文件路径、环境变量或代码块。"

#: ../../advanced/i18n.md:22
msgid ""
"**Be consistent with terminology**: pick one Chinese term per core concept "
"and reuse it everywhere; add new terms intentionally (not ad hoc)."
msgstr "**术语一致**：每个核心概念选定一个中文译法并全站复用；新增术语要有意识地引入（避免临时起意）。"

#: ../../advanced/i18n.md:23
msgid ""
"**Prefer clarity over literalness**: when English is terse, use natural "
"Chinese but keep it concise."
msgstr "**清晰优先于直译**：英文很简洁时，用自然中文表达，但保持简洁。"

