#: ../../advanced/i18n.md:77
msgid ""
"Keep filenames the same across languages; Sphinx switches text via catalogs, "
"not via separate source trees."
msgstr ""
"各语言的源文件名保持一致；Sphinx 通过 catalog 切换文本，而不是维护多份源文件"
"树。"

#: ../../advanced/i18n.md:78
msgid ""
"Raw HTML blocks (``.. raw:: html``) are not extracted for translation. "
"Prefer normal reStructuredText/Markdown text for translatable UI copy."
msgstr ""
"Raw HTML 块（`.. raw:: html`）不会被抽取用于翻译。可翻译的 UI 文案请优先使用"
"普通 reStructuredText/Markdown 文本。"

#: ../../advanced/i18n.md:79
msgid ""
"Avoid translating code blocks unless you *really* want localized code "
"comments/output."
msgstr "除非你确实需要本地化代码注释/输出，否则尽量不要翻译代码块。"

